skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sounds of forest
des:
Fall into a deep sleep with our dreamy forest sounds. Sounds of Forest is the ultimate science-backed companion for relaxation, focus, and better sleep. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Sounds of Forest, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
